00:50:56,700 --> 00:50:58,300
Come on, sweetie. Let's go.

806
00:50:59,000 --> 00:51:00,000
Hey, King.

807
00:51:01,200 --> 00:51:02,200
No, I'm the king. You're the king.

808
00:51:02,300 --> 00:51:04,300
Don't do it, Elvis!
Don't jump.

809
00:51:05,800 --> 00:51:07,300
Mr. Kingman?

810
00:51:08,700 --> 00:51:10,200
Oh, no. Peyton.

811
00:51:11,700 --> 00:51:12,600
Hey.

812
00:51:12,800 --> 00:51:16,700
Yeah, I guess practice ran a little
longer than expected. Thanks, Bo.

813
00:51:16,800 --> 00:51:18,900
- Mr. Kingman, we need to talk about...
- You know what?

814
00:51:19,000 --> 00:51:21,800
Why don't you just call me Joe?

815
00:51:23,500 --> 00:51:24,600
Stop it. Stop it.

816
00:51:24,700 --> 00:51:27,800
Mr. Kingman,
I informed you from the start

817
00:51:27,900 --> 00:51:30,200
