00:52:08,800 --> 00:52:11,200
- Listen, I care about Peyton.
- Then prove it!

831
00:52:11,300 --> 00:52:13,700
- I got it.
- Hey, sweetie!

832
00:52:13,800 --> 00:52:15,500
Your father here was telling me
how excited he is

833
00:52:15,600 --> 00:52:19,100
to finally fulfill the commitment
he made to support the school.

834
00:52:19,200 --> 00:52:22,100
And guess what?
I've got the perfect job for him.

835
00:52:22,200 --> 00:52:23,200
Cool.

836
00:52:23,300 --> 00:52:26,500
No, no, no. Absolutely not.
You're completely insane.

