00:52:34,100 --> 00:52:36,600
No, what I'm telling you is
I am a serious athlete.

840
00:52:36,700 --> 00:52:38,200
Not a ballerina.

841
00:52:38,600 --> 00:52:40,900
<i>You do me a favor, mamita?
